WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:06.020
Subtitle Provide by dramacool.in Translator [Admin.@YNG]

00:00:06.820 --> 00:00:08.620
=Destiny of the General's Bride=

00:00:09.100 --> 00:00:12.020
=Episode 2=

00:00:17.519 --> 00:00:18.160
Qing Yan.

00:00:19.079 --> 00:00:19.679
Qing Yan.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:20.559
Qing Yan.

00:00:30.519 --> 00:00:31.640
You want revenge.

00:00:32.960 --> 00:00:34.240
Is it because

00:00:35.119 --> 00:00:36.320
Xiao Ye

00:00:37.640 --> 00:00:38.600
once defiled you?

00:00:43.600 --> 00:00:45.600
That has nothing to do with you.

00:00:47.719 --> 00:00:49.399
Why should you care?

00:00:55.600 --> 00:00:56.240
Qing Yan,

00:00:57.799 --> 00:00:58.479
I'm sorry.

00:00:59.719 --> 00:01:00.880
I frightened you just now.

00:01:04.439 --> 00:01:05.840
Since Hua told you

00:01:05.840 --> 00:01:06.920
her secret,

00:01:07.760 --> 00:01:09.239
I'll trust you.

00:01:10.840 --> 00:01:12.439
But Hua means everything

00:01:13.840 --> 00:01:15.040
to me.

00:01:16.519 --> 00:01:17.840
Could you tell me

00:01:18.560 --> 00:01:19.400
where she is?

00:01:20.680 --> 00:01:21.760
Take me to her.

00:01:32.640 --> 00:01:34.920
But we had a deal.

00:01:37.000 --> 00:01:38.040
Marry me,

00:01:39.200 --> 00:01:41.439
and I'll tell you about Su Hua.

00:01:44.640 --> 00:01:45.273
(Two days earlier)
You risked your life

00:01:45.274 --> 00:01:46.560
(Two days earlier)
to save me at the dilapidated temple,

00:01:46.560 --> 00:01:47.280
(Mochun Gambling House)

00:01:47.280 --> 00:01:49.359
tricked my gambling brother
into losing everything,

00:01:50.040 --> 00:01:52.359
then lured me here with news of Hua.

00:01:53.079 --> 00:01:54.719
After all this trouble,

00:01:55.359 --> 00:01:57.120
what do you really want?

00:01:57.680 --> 00:01:59.040
Do you mean to kill me?

00:01:59.040 --> 00:02:00.159
Where is Hua?

00:02:01.519 --> 00:02:02.319
If you won't say,

00:02:02.840 --> 00:02:04.239
I'll make you

00:02:04.840 --> 00:02:06.000
live in torment.

00:02:20.680 --> 00:02:21.520
Are you out of your mind?

00:02:23.680 --> 00:02:25.120
What on earth do you want?

00:02:28.439 --> 00:02:29.719
Revenge, of course.

00:02:30.719 --> 00:02:32.039
Can't you see that?

00:02:33.319 --> 00:02:34.520
Either kill me,

00:02:35.240 --> 00:02:36.479
or marry me.

00:02:37.319 --> 00:02:38.919
Otherwise, you'll never know

00:02:39.240 --> 00:02:41.719
where Su Hua is.

00:02:42.000 --> 00:02:42.879
Ridiculous.

00:02:44.840 --> 00:02:47.520
You think I'd let you into my house
to run wild?

00:02:47.719 --> 00:02:49.080
General,

00:02:49.080 --> 00:02:50.840
stop pretending.

00:02:51.120 --> 00:02:53.240
Your mother was tortured to death

00:02:53.240 --> 00:02:54.479
by Grand Madam Xiao.

00:02:55.080 --> 00:02:57.039
Since childhood,

00:02:57.039 --> 00:02:59.719
you've also suffered
under her and Xiao Ye.

00:03:00.280 --> 00:03:01.240
If not for

00:03:01.240 --> 00:03:02.960
rescuing the princess,

00:03:03.719 --> 00:03:05.879
Grand Madam Xiao wouldn't have
petitioned the court

00:03:05.879 --> 00:03:08.599
to place your mother's tablet

00:03:09.400 --> 00:03:11.319
in the ancestral hall,

00:03:11.319 --> 00:03:13.490
and you wouldn't even have been
acknowledged as a Xiao now, would you?

00:03:14.080 --> 00:03:15.960
If you now tell me

00:03:16.240 --> 00:03:17.960
you treat Grand Madam Xiao and Xiao Ye

00:03:17.960 --> 00:03:19.680
as family

00:03:20.719 --> 00:03:23.039
and don't want me
to cause trouble in this house,

00:03:23.719 --> 00:03:25.879
that's the last thing I'd believe.

00:03:26.319 --> 00:03:27.759
You sure know a great deal.

00:03:29.000 --> 00:03:30.759
I know no less

00:03:31.400 --> 00:03:33.080
than Su Hua does.

00:03:33.080 --> 00:03:35.000
But my wife can only be Su Hua.

00:03:40.159 --> 00:03:41.639
After I marry into the Xiao Residence,

00:03:42.280 --> 00:03:43.719
whether I succeed or fail,

00:03:44.439 --> 00:03:45.599
I'll divorce you

00:03:46.039 --> 00:03:47.479
in six months.

00:03:48.319 --> 00:03:50.039
I believe you know
Su Hua's handwriting

00:03:50.479 --> 00:03:52.080
better than I do.

00:03:55.800 --> 00:03:57.319
(Please carry out)

00:03:57.479 --> 00:03:58.719
(the favor Qing Yan asks of you.)

00:03:59.319 --> 00:04:00.639
(In this world,)

00:04:00.919 --> 00:04:02.280
(the only person I trust)

00:04:02.520 --> 00:04:04.080
(is Qing Yan.)

00:04:04.680 --> 00:04:06.039
To show my sincerity,

00:04:06.599 --> 00:04:07.800
on the wedding night,

00:04:08.520 --> 00:04:09.520
I'll tell you something

00:04:09.520 --> 00:04:11.000
about Su Hua.

00:04:12.400 --> 00:04:13.039
What do you say?

00:04:15.800 --> 00:04:16.439
Fine.

00:04:22.360 --> 00:04:23.720
Su Hua

00:04:25.240 --> 00:04:26.839
doesn't want to see you.

00:04:31.959 --> 00:04:32.759
General,

00:04:33.920 --> 00:04:36.199
until I've secured my place
in the Xiao family,

00:04:37.120 --> 00:04:38.800
she won't see you.

00:04:40.959 --> 00:04:41.839
So you'd better

00:04:41.839 --> 00:04:43.399
help me.

00:04:44.480 --> 00:04:45.240
Perhaps

00:04:47.120 --> 00:04:49.399
you two may meet soon.

00:05:19.600 --> 00:05:21.720
(Please review, General)
General, I've searched the registries.

00:05:21.720 --> 00:05:22.720
(Cui Liang)
She wasn't found.

00:05:23.279 --> 00:05:24.199
This Qing Yan

00:05:24.279 --> 00:05:26.439
seems to have appeared out of nowhere,

00:05:26.800 --> 00:05:27.480
but I found

00:05:27.639 --> 00:05:28.600
she and Miss Su

00:05:28.959 --> 00:05:30.480
were once seen in the mountains.

00:05:31.839 --> 00:05:32.680
Mountains?

00:05:34.839 --> 00:05:37.560
There's a woman who lives here, Miss Yu.

00:05:38.160 --> 00:05:39.199
She's

00:05:39.319 --> 00:05:40.319
a physician,

00:05:40.680 --> 00:05:42.639
but she only treats women.

00:05:43.600 --> 00:05:44.639
I sent men to investigate.

00:05:44.720 --> 00:05:45.879
The house is empty.

00:05:47.879 --> 00:05:49.800
This place is clearly cleaned.

00:05:50.480 --> 00:05:51.879
Someone lives here.

00:06:17.439 --> 00:06:18.759
We barely know each other.

00:06:19.360 --> 00:06:21.720
Could this be a misunderstanding?

00:06:22.279 --> 00:06:23.079
Misunderstanding?

00:06:23.839 --> 00:06:25.920
You abandoned Miss Su for the princess.

00:06:26.279 --> 00:06:27.959
Do you have no shame?

00:06:34.959 --> 00:06:35.879
You knew Hua?

00:06:36.879 --> 00:06:38.000
Could you tell me

00:06:38.560 --> 00:06:39.279
where she is?

00:06:41.279 --> 00:06:42.720
Shouldn't you be preparing

00:06:42.720 --> 00:06:44.160
to become the prince consort?

00:06:44.600 --> 00:06:45.720
What are you doing here?

00:06:46.319 --> 00:06:47.920
I never wished to marry the princess.

00:06:50.079 --> 00:06:52.000
Swear to Heaven if you dare.

00:06:56.639 --> 00:06:58.839
Swear in your mother's name.

00:07:03.600 --> 00:07:04.720
Heaven above,

00:07:06.160 --> 00:07:07.720
the only wife in my heart

00:07:08.439 --> 00:07:09.759
is Su Hua.

00:07:11.040 --> 00:07:12.360
Though I take Qing Yan as my wife,

00:07:13.279 --> 00:07:15.120
it's only to find out
Su Hua's whereabouts.

00:07:15.759 --> 00:07:17.360
And I'll never marry the princess.

00:07:18.720 --> 00:07:19.879
If I break this oath,

00:07:20.920 --> 00:07:21.920
may I

00:07:22.879 --> 00:07:24.759
and my late mother

00:07:25.680 --> 00:07:28.040
suffer endless torment

00:07:28.680 --> 00:07:29.959
and never find peace.

00:07:32.639 --> 00:07:33.839
But Miss Su

00:07:36.360 --> 00:07:37.600
has already died.

00:07:40.199 --> 00:07:41.040
What did you say?

00:07:42.780 --> 00:07:47.060
(Tomb of Dearest Friend, Su Hua.
Erected by Miss Yu)

00:08:16.079 --> 00:08:17.000
Hua.

00:08:21.040 --> 00:08:22.120
A year ago,

00:08:23.279 --> 00:08:25.120
Miss Su waited for you
at the Mid-lake Pavilion,

00:08:25.120 --> 00:08:26.519
where you pledged your love.

00:08:27.380 --> 00:08:30.580
(One year earlier)

00:08:39.000 --> 00:08:39.759
Who are you?

00:08:40.759 --> 00:08:41.720
Who am I?

00:08:42.200 --> 00:08:43.639
I'm Xiao Yun's brother.

00:08:43.799 --> 00:08:45.320
Have you not heard about me?

00:08:46.960 --> 00:08:47.799
Brother?

00:08:48.960 --> 00:08:50.240
Seems like Xiao Yun

00:08:50.799 --> 00:08:53.679
hasn't told you about his family.

00:08:54.120 --> 00:08:56.080
Does he truly mean to marry you?

00:08:58.559 --> 00:08:59.840
Unlike your sister,

00:09:00.480 --> 00:09:02.399
she told me who you wrote to

00:09:02.480 --> 00:09:03.600
and when you wrote.

00:09:03.840 --> 00:09:05.320
She told me everything.

00:09:05.600 --> 00:09:06.519
That is

00:09:06.840 --> 00:09:08.519
true heart.

00:09:10.360 --> 00:09:11.159
Man'er?

00:09:12.120 --> 00:09:12.879
That's right.

00:09:13.960 --> 00:09:15.519
Man'er is about to marry me.

00:09:16.240 --> 00:09:18.279
You should be happy for her.

00:09:19.759 --> 00:09:20.480
Say,

00:09:21.399 --> 00:09:22.200
do you know

00:09:22.799 --> 00:09:25.200
why Xiao Yun didn't return to Jiangzhou?

00:09:25.639 --> 00:09:28.200
He went to rescue Princess Zhaoping.

00:09:29.039 --> 00:09:31.000
They say Princess Zhaoping

00:09:31.399 --> 00:09:34.799
is a rare beauty.

00:09:35.480 --> 00:09:36.840
Do you think,

00:09:37.240 --> 00:09:38.720
when Yun saw her,

00:09:39.159 --> 00:09:41.120
would he still care about

00:09:41.120 --> 00:09:42.960
a lowly merchant's
illegitimate daughter?

00:09:48.200 --> 00:09:49.000
You're lying.

00:09:50.919 --> 00:09:51.960
Then tell me,

00:09:53.440 --> 00:09:55.840
why do I have your letters to Xiao Yun?

00:09:57.840 --> 00:09:58.759
And why didn't he

00:09:59.039 --> 00:10:00.720
come to meet you?

00:10:08.960 --> 00:10:10.480
You're more interesting

00:10:10.480 --> 00:10:11.759
than those who only cry.

00:10:35.320 --> 00:10:38.919
Miss Su and I were defiled by Xiao Ye.

00:10:39.639 --> 00:10:41.840
Just because his godfather
is the King of Xiling,

00:10:42.679 --> 00:10:43.879
he has no regard for the law.

00:10:45.600 --> 00:10:47.039
I couldn't conceive,

00:10:47.279 --> 00:10:49.279
so he beat me.

00:10:50.360 --> 00:10:52.720
He even locked me up in the woodshed.

00:10:53.679 --> 00:10:55.639
I was living worse than a dog.

00:10:58.440 --> 00:11:00.080
Miss Su suffered the same,

00:11:01.120 --> 00:11:02.240
just like me.

00:11:04.200 --> 00:11:06.600
She was waiting for you.

00:11:07.279 --> 00:11:08.720
She was proud

00:11:09.360 --> 00:11:10.720
and refused to bend,

00:11:11.840 --> 00:11:12.879
so she endured a lot

00:11:13.840 --> 00:11:15.720
for three months.

00:11:22.279 --> 00:11:23.120
Yun...

00:11:24.600 --> 00:11:26.480
Yun won't let you off.

00:11:28.960 --> 00:11:31.320
You've been calling for him
for three months.

00:11:31.600 --> 00:11:33.200
Has he ever come to save you?

00:11:35.159 --> 00:11:36.360
Even if

00:11:37.000 --> 00:11:38.080
he did,

00:11:38.679 --> 00:11:39.799
we'd never recognize

00:11:39.799 --> 00:11:41.240
a mistress like you.

00:11:42.799 --> 00:11:43.559
Physician,

00:11:44.440 --> 00:11:45.480
take her pulse.

00:12:10.240 --> 00:12:11.360
You wench,

00:12:11.639 --> 00:12:13.000
how dare you hurt me?

00:12:14.720 --> 00:12:16.320
I'll beat you to death.

00:12:18.000 --> 00:12:18.720
Wench!

00:12:19.120 --> 00:12:19.799
Wench!

00:12:20.240 --> 00:12:20.919
How's it?

00:12:21.639 --> 00:12:22.320
Wench!

00:12:22.919 --> 00:12:23.879
Grand Madam Xiao,

00:12:24.240 --> 00:12:25.120
she's not with child.

00:12:26.159 --> 00:12:27.759
To think a lowly merchant's daughter

00:12:27.919 --> 00:12:29.039
could win Xiao Yun's heart.

00:12:30.080 --> 00:12:31.679
I thought she was something else,

00:12:32.440 --> 00:12:34.039
but she's just as worthless.

00:12:35.279 --> 00:12:36.120
Sell her off.

00:12:39.039 --> 00:12:41.120
Xiao Yun is proud and ruthless.

00:12:41.759 --> 00:12:43.440
He might fight back.

00:12:43.720 --> 00:12:44.480
If we keep her alive,

00:12:44.639 --> 00:12:46.000
I'm afraid there could be trouble.

00:12:48.159 --> 00:12:49.399
That makes sense.

00:12:50.879 --> 00:12:51.960
In that case,

00:12:54.519 --> 00:12:55.320
cut her down.

00:13:00.679 --> 00:13:01.840
You're already

00:13:02.639 --> 00:13:05.200
a lamb in our hands,

00:13:05.440 --> 00:13:07.279
but you still have a temper.

00:13:07.799 --> 00:13:09.120
I'll show you

00:13:09.879 --> 00:13:11.120
what I'm capable of.

00:13:16.559 --> 00:13:17.000
Wench!

00:13:17.080 --> 00:13:18.480
I won't forgive you!

00:13:19.039 --> 00:13:19.679
Wench!

00:13:20.200 --> 00:13:20.799
Wench!

00:13:21.440 --> 00:13:21.960
Wench!

00:13:22.879 --> 00:13:23.480
Wench!

00:13:24.080 --> 00:13:24.639
Wench!

00:13:33.320 --> 00:13:34.600
You'll get your retribution.

00:13:35.120 --> 00:13:36.679
You will!

00:13:36.960 --> 00:13:37.799
Here you go.

00:13:59.240 --> 00:14:00.080
Bury her.

00:14:08.279 --> 00:14:09.000
Hua.

00:14:10.919 --> 00:14:11.759
Hua.

00:14:13.960 --> 00:14:14.679
Hua.

00:14:23.620 --> 00:14:25.240
(Nan Jiang)

00:14:25.240 --> 00:14:26.039
Hua,

00:14:26.799 --> 00:14:29.240
you didn't have to marry him.

00:14:34.840 --> 00:14:35.840
Don't worry.

00:14:36.559 --> 00:14:37.759
I can protect myself

00:14:39.879 --> 00:14:41.159
when facing him.

00:14:43.200 --> 00:14:44.840
I have faith in you.

00:14:45.039 --> 00:14:45.879
But

00:14:46.120 --> 00:14:47.840
you once loved him,

00:14:47.919 --> 00:14:49.159
and were about to marry him.

00:14:49.360 --> 00:14:50.679
Given the situation now,

00:14:50.840 --> 00:14:52.120
you must face him every day

00:14:52.120 --> 00:14:53.159
with a new face.

00:14:53.519 --> 00:14:54.519
Isn't that

00:14:54.679 --> 00:14:56.200
torment for you?

00:15:11.399 --> 00:15:12.639
Su Hua is dead.

00:15:13.480 --> 00:15:14.559
Now,

00:15:15.200 --> 00:15:16.440
I'm Qing Yan.

00:15:17.120 --> 00:15:17.919
Qing Yan,

00:15:19.200 --> 00:15:20.759
Mother is asking for you.

00:15:39.460 --> 00:15:43.180
♪Mountains and rivers rise and fall♪

00:15:43.180 --> 00:15:46.380
♪The vast sea opens wide♪

00:15:47.380 --> 00:15:50.380
♪Thank you for staying with me♪

00:15:50.380 --> 00:15:54.460
♪To witness all the lights of the world♪

00:15:55.020 --> 00:15:59.220
♪I remember by the old tree in Qing Yan♪

00:15:59.820 --> 00:16:02.260
♪When we first met♪

00:16:02.900 --> 00:16:09.980
♪Looking back, no more words are needed♪

00:16:10.380 --> 00:16:14.860
♪You went left, I went right♪

00:16:14.860 --> 00:16:18.940
♪If we hadn't met,
there'd be nothing to seek♪

00:16:19.620 --> 00:16:23.260
♪In this long, dusty road of life♪

00:16:23.260 --> 00:16:26.860
♪Love and hate poured
in a single jar of wine♪

00:16:26.860 --> 00:16:30.740
♪Whose heart does love truly claim♪

00:16:30.740 --> 00:16:35.060
♪Yet it yields to just one greeting♪

00:16:35.900 --> 00:16:39.260
♪Gentle longing flows into the river♪

00:16:39.260 --> 00:16:45.060
♪When dreams break,
we will guard each other still♪